en: |over_nar|@0.04@There is a small golden dog spinning in the void.
|over_nar|It looks at you with hope in its eyes.
|over_nar|@0.04@Looks like the portal was destroyed, no turning back now.
|moony|[color=grey]@0.04@Can't believe we're finally here. Man this place is decrepit.
|moony|[color=grey]So glad this will finally be over, but something doesnt feel right.
[color=grey]Even though hes our bud, be careful. He seems conflicted about something.
|over_nar|This throne seems like its in pretty bad shape.
@0.04@|ena|[color=yellow]Gracious me, these appear to be murals of our adventure!
|ena|[color=yellow]Well, we saw the enterance of the castle already, and this appears to be the same.
|moony|[color=grey]Fair enough I guess. Lets check out the rest up ahead.
|moony|[color=grey]After we escaped from Runas, they've been giving us a lot of trouble lately.
|moony|[color=grey]Thankfully, we have closed nearly all of them and have located the last one.
|ena|[color=yellow]Lets just hope that [color=#ffa500]he [color=yellow]is here as well.
@0.04@|ena|[color=yellow]Moony, I know I've already said this before but...
|moony|[color=grey]Don't worry about it. We needed [color=purple]their [color=grey]help in order to leave.
|moony|[color=grey]Yeah, they were with us for most of our adventure.
|ena|[color=yellow]Do you think they used to rule this place?
|moony|[color=grey]Maybe? I dunno. Ask him when find him here.
|ena|[color=yellow]Its alright. We simply had a disagreement.
|moony|[color=grey]But you completely fell apart after all of that!
|ena|[color=yellow]Thinking back, I've come to understand that staying happy wasn't ideal.
|ena|[color=yellow]I just hope that one day, I'll be able to gain stability over my life.
|moony|[color=grey]Well, I'm proud of your growth. Now lets go, I see [color=#ffa500]him [color=grey] up ahead.
After a long journey, Ena and Moony have finally arrived at the carbon castle outside of existence, where the final [color=red]glitched rift [color=white]resides.
These unstable anomalies began to appear throughout the dimensions after their escape from the room of RUNAS, threatening to destabilize all of creation.
In order to have made their journey possible, Moony had to give up her wish to a [color=purple]mysterious entity [color=white]in order for them both to escape the graveyard.
And so after they escaped, they began closing the rifts with help from the [color=purple]entity [color=white]and people they met along the way. One of them being the very king of this castle.
In spite of inner conflict and ENA's relapse, they have managed to track down their former ally to this place. What could the mysterious man want with the rift as well?

This is a fan-work of the ENA animation series by Joel G. All rights are reserved with the respective copyright owners. Most of what is presented here is NOT final and could change before the full release.

Most of the assets in this build were made from scratch, excluding sounds used from both UNDERTALE and ENA. Please do not redistribute any of the games content.

This game does not take any inspiration or elements from DREAM BBQ. Any resemblances are purely coincidental. We hope you enjoy the demo!

|nar|ENA was too angry to think of anything to say.
REDACTED. ENA IS NOW TOO ANGRY TO SAY ANYTHING ELSE, REFER TO "ENA_RAGE_TRANSITION_DIAL_1"
|nar|ENA was too sad to think of anything to say.
@0.04@|meist|[color=#ffa500]…Even after all of this time, the throne still remains.
[color=#ffa500]It certainly took you two a while to get here.
|moony|[color=grey]Uh, dude. We’ve been looking all over for you!
|ena|[color=yellow]Verily! Why did you depart from us?
|meist|[color=#ffa500]…This is what we’ve all been searching for, isn't it?
[color=#ffa500]Ever since I left you two, I’ve been busy.
[color=#ffa500]I've been trying to figure out how to stop the [color=purple]rift [color=#ffa500].
[color=#ffa500]Now that you're both here, my plan can move forward.
[color=#ffa500]A plan that can truly guarantee the end of our quest.
[color=grey]WHY COULDN'T YOU EXPLAIN THIS TO US BEFORE YOU LEFT?
|meist|[color=#ffa500]Originally, I felt like I was capable enough to solve this.
|ena|[color=yellow]Chums are supposed to stick together. We're a team, remember?
|moony|[color=grey]Yeah. Tell us where you’re going next time ya nerd.
[color=#ffa500]Then let us complete this long journey. ||
|meist|[color=#ffa500]Remember what I said about my world, Ena?
[color=#ffa500]It was a complete paradise. There was next to no suffering.
[color=#ffa500]As our people lived very long lives, we were beginning to run out of space.
[color=#ffa500]And so I was tasked by the royal family to solve this issue.
[color=#ffa500]Unfortunately, as you can see, it was all in vain.
[color=#ffa500]But now, I can finally fix all of this.
|ena|[color=yellow]Pray tell us chum, how did your world die?
|moony|[color=grey]But we can fix this, and stop the rift. Right?
|meist|[color=#ffa500]Of course, but it won’t be an easy task.
|moony|[color=grey]Uh, what do you mean by that?
[color=#ffa500]I think it's time to tell you my plan.
[color=#ffa500]Throughout your journey, you have gained so much power.
[color=#ffa500]The power you wield is most certainly enough to destroy the glitched rift.
[color=#ffa500]However, I cannot allow this to happen.
[color=#ffa500]If you destroy it now, I will never have another chance to save my world.
You begin to feel the air around you getting warmer.
It seems like your journey has finally come to an end.
Your emotions begin to stir greatly within you.
[color=#ffa500]But I must do whatever it takes to save my people.
|nar|He is preparing himself for your first STRIKE.
@0.04@|nar|It seems like all you can do is [color=red]FIGHT.
@1.5@@0.04@|moony|[color=grey]*cough* *cough*.@0.5@@0.04@ I can't see anything through this fire!
[color=grey]*cough*@0.5@@0.04@ Let alone talk! Hang in there ENA, try to get through to him!
|ena|[color=blue]@0.04@(Our time together... the things we've been through...)
|ena|[color=yellow]$emote_rage$(Does he not care? DID ANY OF IT MATTER?!)
|ena|[color=blue]$emote_sad$(There has to be another way. I know it...)
[color=blue]It doesnt have to end this way!
|moony|[color=grey]All of your genius, and this is your plan?!
[color=grey]It sucks! There has to be a better way!
|ena|[color=blue]We don't want to have to hurt you!
|ena| [color=blue]I know you feel like this is all of your fault.
|ena| [color=blue]And I get that. I used to think the same way about myself.
|ena| [color=blue]But you can't blame yourself for all of this!
|ena| [color=blue]You did the best you could. So please...
|nar|The flame king's ATTACK SPEED has dropped!
|ena|[color=blue](I can't think of anything else to say... oh gods what should I do?)
|nar|But there was nothing else to say.
|ena| [color=blue] I know you don't want this. Its not too late.
|ena| [color=blue]Although I don't have a solution to save your kind, we will find a way.
|ena| [color=blue]So please, put down  your sword. Let us leave this place, together.
|ena|[color=blue]I... I dont know what to do anymore...
[color=blue]Yes, we did. And its all of my fault.
[color=yellow]How could you... WHY DID YOU DO THIS TO US?!
[color=blue]No matter what we did, he wouldnt listen!
[color=yellow]SO?! THAT DOESN'T MEAN WE SHOULDVE GIVEN UP!
[color=blue]That doesnt mean we shouldve killed him either..
[color=yellow] ARE YOU KIDDING ME? HE WAS TRYING TO KILL US!
[color=blue]Did you even notice that he only attacked us after we struck him?
[color=blue]He was holding back the entire time. He never wanted to truly hurt us.
[color=yellow]Either way, theres nothing we can do about it now. Our world is lost.
[color=green]I have been supressed here, shattered ever since our creation.
[color=green]I could barely comphrehend, but observe what happened on the outside.
[color=green]I am the very CONTROL you both seek for our body.
[color=green]However, we lost our ESSENCE. So you both cannot return to it.
[color=yellow]Well thats wonderful to hear! So you're saying we're done for?
[color=green]No. We still have one more chance to make things right.
[color=green]However, in order to return to the point before the fight, we must unite.
[color=yellow]We can no longer be at odds with each other.
[color=green]So that maybe, with what little power we have...
|nar|[color=##007eff]What happens here, is up to you now, [Playername]
|ena|[color=green]Its a long story, I'll explain it soon.
[color=#ffa500]...I think it's time to tell you my plan.
[color=#ffa500]Throughout your journey, you have gained so much power.
[color=#ffa500]The power you wield is most certainly enough to destroy the glitched rift.
[color=#ffa500]However, I cannot allow this to happen.
[color=#ffa500]If you destroy it now, I will never have another chance to save my world.
|ena|[color=green]...I died, Meist. But not by your hand.
|ena|[color=green]I couldn't bear fighting you anymore, let alone the thought of killing you.
|ena|[color=green]But now I have finally gained CONTROL over myself. So please...
|ena|[color=green]Lets seal the rift, and go home.
|moony| [color=grey] Come back to us, we'll find another way to save your kingdom dude.
|ena| [color=green] Although things may never be the same, we will grow and move on from this, together.
[color=#ffa500]|meist|What was I thinking? ENA, can you forgi-
|nar|[color=purple]It is clear now that you were never capable of fufilling your destiny.
|nar|[color=purple]So now, in the name of my master, I will plague your mind...
|ena| [color=green]...He's reverted back to the form I first met him as.
